sentences.english: Governments waste a lot of breath on their plans to make the economy more competitive.
sentences.chinese: 政府在使经济更具竞争性方面的计划白费了很多唇舌。

sentences.english: In Germany people would like, I don't know, be more competitive.
sentences.chinese: 在德国人们会，我不知道，更有竞争性。

sentences.english: Nearlly all the sports practices nowadays are competitve.
sentences.chinese: 现在开展的体育与东几乎都是竞争性的。

sentences.english: Tungstate competitively inhibits the utilization of molybdenum for the formation of xanthine dehydrogenases.
sentences.chinese: 钨酸盐竞争性地抑制钼的利用以形成黄嘌呤脱氢酶。

sentences.english: The demand of fast progress is linked to competitive sports.
sentences.chinese: 具竞争性的运动常要球选手要快速的进步。

sentences.english: His solo quickly evolved into competition.
sentences.chinese: 独奏很快演变成竞争性的比赛。

sentences.english: China belongs to make the country singly , but the system of government of China is competitive.
sentences.chinese: 中国属于单一制国家，但中国的政府体系是竞争性的。

sentences.english: At the same time, inhibition kinetic constant of noncompetitive inhibition is testified by force of a experiment.
sentences.chinese: 同时选择非竞争性抑制进行了试验验证和常数求解。

sentences.english: The uptake of choline was also competitively inhibited by ethanolamine.
sentences.chinese: 乙醇胺竞争性地抑制胆碱摄取，且存在剂量依赖关系。

sentences.english: An imbalanced game simply does not make a good spectator sport or competitive game.
sentences.chinese: 一款缺乏平衡性的游戏无法被称为有竞争性的游戏。

sentences.english: A deregulated electricity market demands competitive Reactive Power Ancillary Service(RPAS).
sentences.chinese: 开放的电力市场要求有竞争性的无功辅助服务。

sentences.english: Public goods are those possess the features of both non-excludable and non-rival.
sentences.chinese: 公共商品是同时具有非排他性和非竞争性的商品。

sentences.english: Enzymatic kinetics analysis indicated that the inhibition is noncompetitive.
sentences.chinese: 动力学分析表明，其抑制作用为非竞争性。

sentences.english: A "competitive struggle" ensued between the two women.
sentences.chinese: “竞争性斗争”在两个女人间接连发生。

sentences.english: This offer is competitive and based on an expanding market..
sentences.chinese: 此报盘着眼于扩大销路而且很有竞争性。

sentences.english: This contract was not competitively procured.
